name: {Sarah} Love Bird Wedding Invitation
description:
These darling love bird-themed wedding invitations offer something a little different for the modern bride and groom. The charming illustration and playful design make invitations ideal for a couple looking to make a whimsical statement about their upcoming wedding. Colors are fully customizable. 

This set includes: one 5x7 wedding invitation, one invitation envelope, one RSVP card and one RSVP envelope. Postcard style RSVP cards are also available, please contact me for more information.

Want to use this design as your save the date? No problem, just contact me to create a listing for you!
